extends baseEmail

block content
  p Hello #{donorName},
  p Your project brief has been successfully saved as a draft.
  p
    strong Project Details:
  ul
    li
      strong Title: 
      | #{projectTitle}
    li
      strong Description: 
      | #{projectDescription}
    li
      strong Budget: 
      | #{budget} NGN
  p You can complete your project brief at any time by logging into your dashboard and editing the draft.
  p Once you're ready to publish the brief, you'll be able to submit it for NGO review and execution.
  p If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.
